Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Home videotaping gets the OK
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xc3w
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 22 Jan 1984
Movie makers lose court action against home video taping. Supreme Court rules no copyright law has been infringed. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less